PresentationColumn.name: Delay Perf % (0=Ontime, >0=Late)
PresentationColumn.Description: Index of Arrival delay expressed as Percentage of Air time. If Air time = 100 and Arr delay = 5, Perf = 5%

PresentationColumn.name: % of Sch Fl Within 30 Min Late
PresentationColumn.Description: Percent of flights that arrive on time. Note: If you select Origin as a category, you get percent of flights that depart from those airports and arrive on time.

Alias.name: % of Sch Fl Arr Less than 30 Min Late
% of Sched Fl Arr Less than 30 Min Late
% of Sched Fl Within 30 Min Arr Delay

PresentationColumn.name: % of Sch Fl Over 30 Min Late
PresentationColumn.Description: Percent of flights that arrive on time. Note: If you select Origin as a category, you get percent of flights that depart from those airports and arrive on time.

Alias.name: % of Sch Fl Arr Over than 30 Min Late
% of Sched Fl Arr Over than 30 Min Late
% of Sched Fl Over 30 Min Arr Delay

PresentationColumn.name: -- Delay Catchup during Flight ----------------
PresentationColumn.Description: Percent of flights that arrive on time. Note: If you select Origin as a category, you get percent of flights that depart from those airports and arrive on time.

PresentationColumn.name: % Delay Increase After Dept
PresentationColumn.Description: % increase of delay after departure. If plane left 10 min late and arrived 15 min late, % increase = 50%

PresentationColumn.name: Diff Arr - Dept Delay
PresentationColumn.Description: Difference in minutes between Arrival and Departure delay. If plane left 10 min late and arrived 15 min late, difference = 5.

PresentationColumn.name: Ratio Arr to Dept Delay
PresentationColumn.Description: Ratio of Arrival dealy in minutes divided by Departure Delay. If plane left 10 min late and arrived 15 min late, ratio = 1.5.
